[[Translation:en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Show vehicle speed]]
A [[en/Community/Patches/Patches|patch]] that displays the current vehicle speed in the vehicle information window.


== Description ==
Once this patch is activated, you'll know at any time how fast your vehicle is moving. The speed will be either displayed in km/h or mph, depending on your [[en/Distance units]]. You can change the distance units in the [[en/Manual/Game options window]].


== Use ==
This feature is enabled by default. You can disable it through the [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Configuring patches/Interface|configure patches -> interface]] window or use the following syntax in [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Openttd.cfg]]:

<pre>
[patches]
vehicle_speed = false
</pre>
